---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { ArrowRight, Star, CheckCircle, XCircle, MessageSquare, Video, Phone, Search, Filter, ExternalLink, DollarSign, Brain, Users } from 'lucide-react';

const platforms = [];
---

<BaseLayout>
<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Best Online Therapy Platforms</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Discover the top-rated online therapy platforms categorized by different needs, preferences, and specialties to find your perfect match.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="/tools/matchers/therapy-platform-matcher" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">Find your perfect therapy match</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Platform Categories */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          {/* General Therapy Platforms */}
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <MessageSquare class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">General Therapy</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Platforms offering a wide range of therapy services for various mental health conditions.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/betterhelp" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  BetterHelp
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/talkspace" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Talkspace
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/calmerry" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Calmerry
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/best/platforms/best-online-therapy-platforms" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">View all general platforms</a>
          </div>
          
          {/* Medication + Therapy */}
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <Brain class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Medication + Therapy</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Platforms that offer both therapy and psychiatric medication management services.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/talkspace" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Talkspace
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/cerebral" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Cerebral
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/brightside" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Brightside
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/best/platforms/best-medication-therapy-platforms" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">View all medication platforms</a>
          </div>
          
          {/* Specialized Platforms */}
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <Users class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Specialized Platforms</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Platforms focusing on specific demographics, conditions, or therapy approaches.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/regain" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  ReGain (Couples)
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/pride-counseling" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Pride Counseling (LGBTQ+)
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                <a href="/reviews/platforms/online-therapy" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                  Online-Therapy.com (CBT)
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/best/platforms/best-specialized-platforms" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">View all specialized platforms</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Featured Platforms */}
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Featured Online Therapy Platforms</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            {platforms.slice(0, 3).map((platform) => (
              <div key={platform.slug} class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img 
                  src={platform.image} 
                  alt={`${platform.name} Review`} 
                  class="w-full min-w-0 h-48 object-cover"
                />
                <div class="p-6">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">{platform.name}</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="mr-1">
                        {renderStars(platform.rating)}
                      </div>
                      <span class="text-gray-600">{platform.rating}/5</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    {platform.description}
                  </p>
                  
                  <div class="mb-4">
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">
                      <strong>Price:</strong> {platform.price}
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                      <strong>Best For:</strong> {platform.bestFor}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                    <Link to={`/reviews/platforms/${platform.slug}`} class="text-indigo-600 font-medium flex items-center hover:text-indigo-800">
                      Read review <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" />
                    </a>
                    <a href={`https://www.${platform.slug.replace('-', '')}.com`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 flex items-center text-sm">
                      Visit site <ExternalLink class="h-3 w-3 ml-1" />
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <a href="/best/platforms/best-online-therapy-platforms" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">View all top-rated platforms</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Platform Comparison */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Platform Comparison</h2>
          
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="min-w-full min-w-0 bg-white">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-gray-100 border-b">
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Platform</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Price Range</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Communication</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Insurance</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Medication</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Rating</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-700 font-semibold">Best For</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                {platforms.map((platform) => (
                  <tr key={platform.slug} class="border-b hover:bg-gray-50">
                    <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">{platform.name}</td>
                    <td class="py-4 px-4">{platform.price}</td>
                    <td class="py-4 px-4">
                      <div class="flex space-x-1">
                        {platform.communication.includes('messaging') && (
                          <MessageSquare class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600" title="Messaging" />
                        )}
                        {platform.communication.includes('video') && (
                          <Video class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600" title="Video" />
                        )}
                        {platform.communication.includes('phone') && (
                          <Phone class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600" title="Phone" />
                        )}
                      </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="py-4 px-4">
                      {platform.insurance ? (
                        <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500" />
                      ) : (
                        <XCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500" />
                      )}
                    </td>
                    <td class="py-4 px-4">
                      {platform.medication ? (
                        <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500" />
                      ) : (
                        <XCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500" />
                      )}
                    </td>
                    <td class="py-4 px-4">
                      <div class="flex">
                        {renderStars(platform.rating)}
                      </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="py-4 px-4 text-sm">{platform.bestFor.split(',')[0]}</td>
                  </tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <a href="/compare/platforms" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">See detailed platform comparisons</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Platform Categories */}
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Find the Right Platform for Your Needs</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            {/* By Price */}
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <DollarSign class="h-5 w-5 text-green-600" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">By Price Range</h3>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/specific-needs/best-affordable-therapy" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Budget-Friendly Options (Under $50/week)
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/specific-needs/mid-range-therapy-options" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Mid-Range Options ($50-$80/week)
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/specific-needs/premium-therapy-services" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Premium Services ($80+/week)
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/specific-needs/best-insurance-coverage" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Best Insurance Coverage
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            {/* By Condition */}
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <Brain class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-600" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">By Condition</h3>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/conditions/best-for-anxiety" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Best for Anxiety
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/conditions/best-for-depression" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Best for Depression
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/conditions/best-for-ptsd" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Best for PTSD
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                  <a href="/best/conditions/best-for-relationships" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    Best for Relationship Issues
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* CTA Section */}
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg p-8 text-white text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Not Sure Which Platform Is Right For You?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Take our personalized assessment to get matched with the perfect online therapy platform based on your unique needs, preferences, and budget.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/tools/matchers/therapy-platform-matcher" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">Find Your Perfect Match</a>
            <a href="/tools/assessments/mental-health-assessment" class="border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-10">Take Mental Health Assessment</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* FAQ Section */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">What's the difference between general and specialized therapy platforms?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                General therapy platforms like BetterHelp and Talkspace offer a wide range of mental health services for various conditions, while specialized platforms focus on specific demographics (like couples or LGBTQ+ individuals) or treatment approaches (like CBT). Specialized platforms often provide therapists with expertise in those specific areas.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">How do I know which platform is right for me?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Consider your specific needs (type of therapy, communication preferences), budget constraints, insurance requirements, and whether you need medication management. Our detailed reviews and comparison tools can help you identify which platform best meets your unique requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Are online therapy platforms as effective as in-person therapy?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Research shows that online therapy can be just as effective as in-person therapy for many conditions, including depression, anxiety, and PTSD. The key is finding a qualified therapist and a platform that offers the communication methods that work best for you.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Which platforms accept insurance?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Talkspace, Cerebral, and Brightside accept insurance from many major providers. BetterHelp and Calmerry don't work directly with insurance companies but may provide receipts for reimbursement. Check our detailed reviews for specific insurance information.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
